'''碧山體育場'''（{{lang-en|Bishan Stadium}}），位于新加坡[[碧山|碧山]]规划区内，于1998年开放。球场可以容纳6254名观众，目前是[[新加坡职业足球联赛|新加坡职业足球联赛]][[內政聯足球俱樂部|內政聯足球俱樂部]]的主场。<ref name="Soccerway 2012"/>

==球场设施==
球场的草坪配有自动浇水系统，也被[[国际足球联合会|国际足球联合会]]比准举办国际比赛。<ref name="AsiaOne, Asias Leading News Portal, Get Latest News at AsiaOne 2009">{{cite web | title=THE WAY AHEAD | website=AsiaOne, Asia's Leading News Portal, Get Latest News at AsiaOne | date=2009-03-24 | url=http://www.asiaone.com/News/The%2BNew%2BPaper/Story/A1Story20090324-130601.html  | accessdate=2018-07-20 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171030165449/http://www.asiaone.com/News/The%2BNew%2BPaper/Story/A1Story20090324-130601.html | archivedate=2017-10-30 | deadurl=no }}</ref>体育场也有也有一条8赛道的[[400米|400米]]塑胶跑步道。体育场傍边还有游泳池，健身室，网球场等设施。<ref name="ActiveSG 2018">{{cite web | title=Bishan Stadium | website=ActiveSG | date=2018-08-18 | url=https://www.myactivesg.com/facilities/bishan-stadium | language=en | access-date=2018-09-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421151031/https://www.myactivesg.com/facilities/bishan-stadium | archive-date=2016-04-21 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="ActiveSG 20181">{{cite web | title=Bishan Swimming Complex | website=ActiveSG | date=2018-08-18 | url=https://www.myactivesg.com/facilities/bishan-swimming-complex | language=en | access-date=2018-09-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714234628/https://www.myactivesg.com/facilities/bishan-swimming-complex | archive-date=2017-07-14 | dead-url=yes }}</ref> 球场附近的重要设施包括[[SMRT地铁|SMRT地铁]]的{{link-en|碧山车厂|Bishan Depot}}，SMRT员工俱乐部也设立在体育场傍边。这两个设施都与碧山體育場共用一条道路。<ref name="SMRT Corporation Ltd 2015">{{cite web | title=Locations | website=SMRT Corporation Ltd | date=2015-02-04 | url=https://www.smrt.com.sg/Our-Business/SMRT-Automotive-Services/Locations | access-date=2018-09-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180727143753/https://smrt.com.sg/Our-Business/SMRT-Automotive-Services/Locations | archive-date=2018-07-27 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==重要赛事==
碧山体育场于[[2010年夏季青年奧林匹克運動會|2010年夏季青年奧林匹克運動會]]作为[[2010年夏季青年奧林匹克運動會田徑比賽|田徑比賽]]的场地。体育场2009年间关闭以便进行翻新，以便主办赛事，并且于2010年10月重新开放。<ref name="Singapore Athletics 2010">{{cite web | title=Day 5 of YOG Athletics | website=Singapore Athletics | date=2010-08-22 | url=http://www.singaporeathletics.org.sg/day-5-of-yog-athletics | access-date=2018-09-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170802010722/http://www.singaporeathletics.org.sg/day-5-of-yog-athletics | archive-date=2017-08-02 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Sport Singapore 2010">{{cite web | title=SSC Facilities Reopen After YOG Closure | website=Sport Singapore | date=2010-10-01 | url=http://www.sportsingapore.gov.sg/newsroom/media-releases/2010/10/ssc-facilities-reopen-after-yog-closure | access-date=2018-09-04 | archive-date=2018-09-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180904222405/https://www.sportsingapore.gov.sg/newsroom/media-releases/2010/10/ssc-facilities-reopen-after-yog-closure | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==公共交通链接==
球场附近交通设施包括[[碧山地铁站|碧山地铁站]]与[[碧山巴士轉換站|碧山巴士轉換站]]。步行约10分中可以抵达体育场。<ref name="ActiveSG 2018"/>

